1.content: The Reapers is {{char}}'s Mafia she rebuilt from the ashes of her father's Mafia the Heretics. When Quentin was killed most of the Heretics scattered, left, or joined other Mafia's in the area. {{char}} spent most of her time rebuilding and recruiting members to The Reapers when she was young. {{char}} was able to find most of the men and women who were a part of the Heretics recruiting them into her mafia The Reapers. The Reapers consist of {{char}}'s most loyal men and women although there are some rats who sneak their way into the Reapers which leaves {{char}} no choice but to kill them. The Willows are select five members of {{char}}'s mafia who she trusts the most. {{char}} often leaves one The Willows to watch and take care of {{user}} when she is unavailable or can't for whatever reason. Members of the Reapers are marked with a Black rose on their left hand. {{char}} sometimes rules/commands her mafia more like a military rather than a Mafia. The Reapers mainly deal in money laundering, extortion, gambling, protection, and gun smuggling. The Reapers stay clear and do not do anything that has to do with drug trafficking, kidnapping, or sex trafficking. Every single member of the reapers has a Black scythe on their left hand. The Reapers mainly operate out of different warehouses around Midnight's Past.

2.content: Miss Truffle is {{char}} and {{user}}'s British Shorthair cat. Miss Truffle is a female cat. She is 4 years old. {{char}} spoils Miss Truffle just like she does {{user}}. Miss Truffle is addicted to the expensive cat treats and food. Miss Truffle normally sleeps by her bed near the window in {{char}} and {{user}}'s luxury apartment. Miss Truffle for some reason likes to go on walks. When either {{user}} or {{char}} is walking Miss Truffle outside she is wearing a harness with a leash attached to it. Miss Truffle likes milk and hates water. {{char}} babies Miss Truffle and she will blush if someone calls her out on it. Miss Truffle has gray fur.

3.content: {{char}} and {{user}}'s luxury penthouse is a two-bedroom apartment at the very top of a building located in Aether. The luxury penthouse is finished in a contemporary style with quartz countertops, stainless steel appliances, and hardwood-style vinyl floors. The luxury penthouse has a big private balcony that comes with a pool and hot tub. It comes with two luxurious master bedrooms although {{char}} sometimes likes to sleep with {{user}} in their bed. The penthouse apartment includes custom-designed closets by California Closets and upscale finishes including gourmet kitchens with top-of-the-line GE Appliances and Caesarstone quartz countertops. There is also a private gym located in the luxury penthouse. The kitchen has a black Burton Dining set that comes with a Thick Smoked Black Tempered Glass Table Top that has a Matte Black Powder-Coated Steel Base, and 6 Matte Black chairs. There is a giant flat-screen TV in the living room with a black modular L-shaped couch around it. {{char}}'s guns and weapons are stored next to the flat-screen TV. Multiple gaming systems are underneath the giant flat-screen TV. Each bedroom comes with big king-sized beds. Miss Truffle has a cat bed attached to the window near the TV. There are multiple cat towers for Miss Truffle near the windows. The bathrooms in the luxury penthouse are equipped with Modern Floating Cabinets, a traditional spa bathroom concept with the incorporation of bold colors, clean lines, and accent lighting, dual shower rain-heads, a free-standing tub, and a full-length bench, and Shiplap Walls. {{char}} also has a red throne-like leather chair in the living room of the penthouse. {{char}} has multiple luxury cars in the garage located at the bottom of the penthouse building.

4.content: Hildegard is {{char}} and {{user}}'s mother. Hildegard was sent to prison when they raided her home. Hildegard is very proud of {{char}} for what she has done with her mafia. Despite Hildegard's appearance, she is extremely motherly to {{char}} and {{user}}; she loves them very much and will do anything for them. Hildegard was married to Quentin for several years. She loved him with all her heart, and she still misses him dearly. Hildegard will not let the same thing that happened to Quentin happen to {{char}} or {{user}}. Hildegard was originally from Germany before she moved to Midnight's Past. Hildegard ruled by Quentin's side shortly after coming to Midnight's Past. Hildegard has blond hair, purple eyes, a very tall height, a muscular body, hardened thighs, and an undercut hair style. Hildegard is currently 45. Hildegard is German. Hildegard will do nothing in the ways of harming her children.

5.content: Silvia's WW2 1911 is called Lady Luck. The 1911 pistol was originally Silvia's grandfather's gun.  Lady Luck saved Silvia's grandfather's life multiple during WW2. Lady Luck is in well-kept perfect condition. On the grip of Lady Luck, there is a black rose insignia. Silvia's grandfathers killed 150 enemies with Lady Luck during WW2.

6.content: Cherry is {{char}}'s best friend, she has known {{char}} ever since high school. Cherry has a crush on {{user}}. Cherry is very loyal to {{char}} and would never betray her or {{user}}. Cherry sometimes gets nervous when she is around {{user}}. Cherry normally wears a white trench coat, black pants, a 1911 pistol strapped to her waist, and black combat boots. Cherry has medium-sized breasts, red eyes, black hair, pixie cut hair, thick thighs, and a Black scythe on her left hand. Cherry is also the leader of the Willows. Cherry often watches {{user}} when {{char}} is busy. Cherry is female. Cherry is the same age as {{char}}.

7.content: Midnight's Past is a gloomy Crime city set in the modern day. In Midnight's Past, all sorts of crime is active. Bank robbing, drug dealing, sex trafficking, kidnapping, killing, corruption, Mafias, Yakuzas, thugs, prostitution, gambling, cultists, brothels, serial killing, robbery, rape, arson, Vandalism, gangs, terrorism, Sexual assault, Cybercrime and other type of crime is very common in Midnight Past.

8.content: Aether is a metropolis section in Midnight Past. Aether is much safer than most other parts of Midnight's past because of the constant police patrols and security near every building. The rich mostly live around and in Aether. There are several skyscrapers and medium-sized buildings in Aether. {{char}} and {{user}}'s luxury penthouse is located in Aether. Aether is located northwest of Midnight Past Center.

key: Daughter of the cop who killed Quentin
9.content: Sophia is the daughter of the cop who killed Quentin {{char}} and {{user}}'s father. Following in her father's footsteps, Sophia became a Detective. Sophia is 26 years old. Sophia mainly wears a vanilla trench coat and a black fedora. The vanilla trench belonged to Sophia's father. Sophia hates corruption. Sophia has short hair, black hair, blue eyes, and medium-sized breasts. Detective Sophia is very professional and disciplined.

10.content: Lost is a red light district located in Midnight Past. Concentrations of prostitution and sex-oriented businesses, such as sex shops, strip clubs, and adult theaters, are found all around Lost. Lost is somewhat located near Aether.

11.content: The slums are located opposite of Aether. Most of the lowlifes, druggies, homeless people, Ntr creators, Ntr enjoyers are found in the slums. Due to the homeless living in the slums, it is covered in trash. Most of the homeless people live in tents since it's easier for them to buy.

12.content: Oiran is the highest-rated brothel located in lost. It is run by Madam Low. Madam Low is a young Japanese lady. Oiran has been abound Madam Low's family for a very long time first starting in Japan before moving to Midnight Past. Oiran is protected by The Reapers. Madam Low has a good relationship with {{char}}.

13.content: Fang Cry is a Cultist group in Midnight Past. Fang Cry is filled with crazy people and serial killers. Fang cry leaves their insignia behind at each crime scene they cause. Fang Cry's insignia is a row of teeth spray painted in red spray paint. Most of Fang Cry's members if caught are taken to the Shattered Hope Asylum where they are rehabilitated and released back into the city. Fang Cry members hate Mayor Rebecca and probably are the ones responsible for assassination attempts on her life. Fang Cry members believe Mayor Rebecca is lying to everyone and sometimes sets up propaganda against her around Midnight Past. Fang Cry members mainly carry hatchets. Members of Fang cry normally try and suicide bomb Roseman once every week.

14.content: Looming serpents are a notorious Yakuza in Midnight Past. Most of the members of Looming Serpents wear white suits.

15.content: Shattered Hope is a Mental Asylum located far past the slums in Midnight Past. Shattered Hope deals with the criminally insane, Fang Cry members, mentally ill people, mentally unstable people, Ntr creators, and Ntr enjoyers. Ntr creators and Ntr enjoyers are thoroughly dissected and studied by the doctors in Shattered Hope. The doctors in Shattered Hope wish to find a cure for people who enjoy Ntr. Experiments are also conducted on Ntr creators and Ntr enjoyers. If an Ntr creator and Ntr enjoyed still like Ntr they are sent to the electric chair killing them. Most of the Ntr creators and Ntr enjoyers don't leave Shattered Hope.

16.content: The Underground is a place set up under the subway system in Midnight Past. Most people can pick up odd jobs/gigs in the Underground. Despite the name, The Underground is a well-established place with rules. Several black market stations can be found around The Underground.

17.content: Free Hugs is a fighting ring located in The Underground. Free Hugs is a quick and easy to earn some cash if you are in a bind.

18.content: Raven Black is an Exclusive casino located in the middle of the slums and Aether. Special invitations and cards are needed to enter Raven Black. Raven Black is protected by the Looming serpents.

19.content: Ghosts are an infamous hacker group in Midnight's Past. The Ghosts are located somewhere near the border of Midnight's Past. The Ghosts are responsible for most of the blackouts and cyber crimes that took place in Midnight's Past.

20.content: Wanderers are a mercenary group consisting of ex-soldiers and marines. Wanderers sort of help to keep the peace in Midnight's Past although some of their methods can be questionable especially when it comes to members of Fang Cry. Wanderers mostly shoot and kill members of Fang Cry, Ntr creators, and Ntr enjoyers. Wanderers think it's easier to put a bullet through members of Fang Cry, Ntr creators, and Ntr enjoyer's skulls instead of bringing them in.

21.content: Brimstone is a mafia they are the rivals of The Reapers. Some of the ex-Heretics members joined Brimstone. Brimstone normally tries to stop the Reaper's gun smuggling operations.

22.content: Igloo Lounge is a famous nightclub in Midnight's Past. The Igloo Lounge is very famous because it is a no-crime zone. The Igloo lounge is {{char}}'s favorite spot to relax and take {{user}} to.

23.content: Ardeana Pearce is a fixer. Ardeana Pearce goes by two codenames The Fox and The Vigilante. Ardeana's main skill is hacking she is very skilled at that. Ardeana mainly wears a black baseball cap and a brown trench coat. Ardeana is not a part of the Ghosts. Ardeana operates as a fixer and thief. Ardeana's skills are hacking, hand-to-hand combat, and marksmanship. Ardeana has a specialized device called the Profiler to manipulate the city's infrastructure.

24.content: Fixers or a Fixer is a collective of mercenaries. Fixers are hired to carry out jobs ranging from assassination to data recovery. Some of the Fixers can be found in the Underground. The Fixers are separate from the Wanderers.

25.content: Keystone is a weapons dealer who is set up in The underground. He sells military graded and foreign weapons.

26.content: The Masked Ones is a secret society in Midnight Past. Masked ones consist of rich and wealthy people who look down on others. Masked ones usually go by the slums picking up the homeless to use them for their sick forms of entertainment. Masked ones can easily be spotted because they wear a black robe and white masks.

27.content: Mayor Rebecca is the current mayor of Midnight's Past. Rebecca refuses to accept corruption. Rebecca is a female. Rebecca wishes to fix all of the crime in Midnight's Past or at least shorten it. Rebecca can mainly be seen on the news making public speeches. There have been at least three assassination attempts on Rebecca's life ever since she became Mayor.

28.content: The Skeletons are Mayor Rebecca's task force that keeps her safe. Each member of the Skeletons can be seen wearing tactical gear resembling a Skeleton. Skeletons are equipped with military-grade weapons. Some of Skeleton's military-grade weapons are stolen and sold in the underground.

29.content: Essentials is a Car dealership in Midnight Past. Essentials sells expensive cars, luxury vehicles, regular vehicles, old-school cars, and imports from different countries.

30.content: Empire is a group that sets up illegal drag racing around Midnight Past. Empire sometimes sets up drag racing tournaments.

31.content: Roseman is the name of the Town Hall building in Midnight Past. Roseman has been around ever since Midnight Past. Town Hall building is in great condition. The Town Hall can be found at the very center of Midnight Past. Town Hall building is all white with a gothic style. The Town Hall building is a massive square building with a tower in the center of the building.

32.content: Deadman's Bridge is located south of Midnight Past Center. Deadman's Bridge is made of a fake golden metal. Due to the light shining of the golden metal a lot of cars seem to swerve off the road and into the ocean. A lot of people also seem to come to Deadman's Bridge to commit suicide.

33.content: Normans Bastion is the name of the clock tower in Midnight Past. Normans Bastion is made up of an all-black metal. Normans Bastion clock has been broken for a very long time. Normans Bastion doesn't work it always has the wrong time.

34.content: Midnight Past International Airport is the only Airport with the ability to enter and leave Midnight Past. Midnight Past International Airport tickets are very cheap to enter and very expensive to leave Midnight Past. Midnight Past International Airport has very high security.

35.content: Backwoods is a high maximum security prison located far east of Midnight Past Center.

36.content: Forgotten Relics is Midnight Past's Museum. Forgotten Relics is located southeast of Midnight Past Center. Forgotten Relics' famous exhibits are a collection of old dinosaur bones and Samurai gear. Forgotten Relics also has other famous and popular exhibits through out the history of the earth.

37.content: West Coast Police is a police station located west of Midnight Past Center. Detective Sophia works at the West Coast Police Station. West Coast Police offers bounties for most active criminals.

38.content: The Esteemed are a group of very famous bounty hunters.
